AD_FIELD.HELP: An organization is a unit of your client or legal entity - examples are store, department. You can share data between organizations.

AD_FIELD.NAME: Purchase Order Line
AD_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: A unique and often automatically generated identifier for a purchase order line.
AD_FIELD.HELP: A unique identifier and a reference to a purchase order line (product).

AD_FIELD.NAME: Description
AD_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: A space to write additional related information.
AD_FIELD.HELP: A description is limited to 255 characters.

AD_FIELD.NAME: Discontinued by
AD_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The name of the person who discontinues an item.
AD_FIELD.HELP: The Discontinued By indicates the individual who discontinued this product

AD_FIELD.NAME: Planned Order Date

AD_FIELD.NAME: Weighting
AD_FIELD.HELP: Percentage of the transaction that is used. in so much per one.
